EQUIV5 = -Dsdot=ddot -Dsasum=dasum -Dsaxpy=daxpy -Dsscal=dscal -Dsnrm2=dnrm2 -Dscopy=dcopy -Dsgbtrf=dgbtrf -Dsgbtrs=dgbtrs -DGRREAL=4

CPP = /lib/cpp -C -traditional -ffreestanding

SOLPSINCLUDE += $(shell pkg-config libtirpc --cflags)
LD_SONNET += $(shell pkg-config libtirpc --libs)

